text: MFK Nová Dubnica is a Slovak football team, based in the town of Nová Dubnica. ==Colours== Club colours are red and white. ==External links== *Official club website *Futbalnet profile *MFK Nová Dubnica at Nová Dubnica portal * ==References== Category:Football clubs in Slovakia Category:Association football clubs established in 1956
